===Noun===
'''{{ARchar|ُُمُحَرّمٌ}}''' (muħárram) {{m}}

#[[Muharram]], the first of the twelve months of the Muslim lunar calendar, each beginning on a [[new moon]]. [[Muharram]] means "forbidden" in Arabic, and it is unlawful to fight during this month.

